  "A spreadsheet user creates a budget model with the following formulas: =SUM(B2:B15) for total expenses, =B1-B16 for surplus, and =B17/B1 for savings rate. If income (B1) is $5,200 and total expenses come to $4,350, what values do the surplus and savings rate cells display?": "",
