  "A financial technology comparison: Tool A is free with ads and sells anonymized data. Tool B costs $99/year with no ads and does not sell data. Tool C is a spreadsheet requiring 2 hours/month of manual entry (valued at $25/hour). Purely on cost-benefit, which is most cost-effective for someone who values privacy and saves $200/month using any tool?": "",
